A weathered stone bridge spanning between two cliffsides, one cliff lush with overgrown ancient ruins covered in moss and vines, the other cliff featuring sleek modern architecture with clean geometric shapes and glass surfaces. A lone figure stands at the midpoint of the bridge, looking toward the modern side. The sky transitions from stormy grey clouds over the old ruins to bright golden sunset light illuminating the new structures. Birds migrate across the sky from old to new. Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures, warm earth tones blending into cool teals and oranges, dreamy atmospheric perspective, gentle wind carrying autumn leaves across the scene.
